A scence based on plato's allegory of the cave rendered using Opengl.

/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/////////////////////////////Controls////////////////////////////////
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
W = Move forward
A = Turn left
S = Move backwards
D = Turn right
Q = Strafe  left
E = Strafe  right
E = Pan up
T = Pan down
F = Tilt down
G = Tilt up
Ctrl = Crouch

All assets have used with the relevant licensing and the creators in no way endorse me or this project. 

A special thanks goes out to all content creators who freely released their models and texture to the public.

The Geisha model is under the Creative Commons 4.0 Unported license and can be found at:
https://resources.blogscopia.com/2010/04/22/geisha-download/
https://resources.blogscopia.com/license-2/

The AppleIIe computer computer model was used under the 'Creative Commons 2.5 Attribution of Spain license' and can be found at:
http://www.esi.uclm.es/museo/index_en.html

The Skybox textures pack is a 'unrestricted asset' from the unity store pushished under an 'Extension Asset' License (a license that I have obtain). The texture pack can be found at:
https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/2d/textures-materials/sky/allsky-free-10-sky-skybox-set-146014
and more information reguarding the 'Asset Store Terms of Service and EULA' can be found at:
https://unity3d.com/legal/as_terms

